{
  "id": "ideam-demo-video-script-storyboard",
  "name": "IdeaM Demo Video — Script & Storyboard",
  "rootNodeId": "demo-root",
  "nodes": {
    "demo-root": {
      "id": "demo-root",
      "name": "IdeaM Demo Video — Script & Storyboard",
      "content": "<p><strong>The one central demo video for IdeaM.</strong> Runtime target: <strong>8–10 minutes</strong>. Visual direction: <strong>light theme</strong> throughout (matches the new marketing site), real content in the content pane the whole way, and every menu shown physically <em>dropping down</em> as it's narrated.</p><p><strong>The story:</strong> Maya Okonkwo, a solo management consultant, has one weekend to turn four scattered sources into a hospital-board recommendation — and every finished deliverable that goes with it. We watch her bring the sources in, let IdeaM merge them into one line of thinking, develop the idea, absorb a client email that changes everything mid-flow, and then fan the single outline out into a slide deck, a podcast, an email, and a social post.</p><p><strong>How to read this file:</strong> one section per scene. Each scene's content holds two blocks — <strong>ON SCREEN</strong> (the storyboard: which menu drops, what's in the content pane, the action, rough duration) and <strong>NARRATION</strong> (the exact voiceover words for a warm, confident human voice to read).</p><p><em>Total narration ≈ 1,460 words · 11 scenes · fits comfortably under 10 minutes.</em></p>",
      "type": "root",
      "parentId": null,
      "childrenIds": [
        "scene-1",
        "scene-2",
        "scene-3",
        "scene-4",
        "scene-5",
        "scene-6",
        "scene-7",
        "scene-8",
        "scene-9",
        "scene-10",
        "scene-11",
        "scene-prod"
      ],
      "prefix": "",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1784908803154,
